                     <interp inst="t18370918-2155-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18370918-cd-113" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18370918-2155-offence-1 t18370918-cd-113"></join>13th of September</rs>, 1 pistol, value 7<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18370918-name-729" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18370918-name-729" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
